<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">זהב</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
זהב /  zâhâb / zaw-hawb'

===Etymology===
From an unused root meaning to shimmer; 

===Noun===
'''זהב'''

# [[gold]]; figuratively something gold colored (that is, yellow), as oil, a clear sky: - gold (-en), fair weather.

